data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prime location of Gainesville! This exceptional property boasts numerous updates throughout, making it truly move-in ready. Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac within an established neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and traditional charm.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail that sets this home apart. The spacious and inviting living spaces have been thoughtfully updated, ensuring both style and functionality. Whether you're relaxing with family or entertaining guests, this home has it all. The partially finished basement provides extra space for your needs. Whether you envision a game room, home office, or a cozy retreat, this versatile area is ready to fulfill your desires. No HOA fees mean you have the freedom to enjoy your property as you wish, and the privacy you deserve. Imagine the possibilities of your own oasis, complete with a private deck for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping, dining, and entertainment, all while residing in a peaceful and friendly neighborhood.
